OL,3,CChamber of Commerce President resigns
OL,4,Cover political donation
OL,6,FThe President of Jersey's Chamber of
OL,7,FCommerce has stepped down after
OL,8,Fdonating money to one of the island's
OL,9,Fpolitical organisations.
OL,11,FLee Madden, who's been in the post for
OL,12,Fa year, announced his resignation
OL,13,Ftoday (4 June 2026), saying the
OL,14,Fdonation was made in a private
OL,15,Fcapacity and was formally declared.
OL,17,FBut pressure from businesses has
OL,18,Fforced him out, although he maintains
OL,19,Fhe was only acting in Jersey's best
OL,20,Finterests.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
