FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1780600264
OL,3,CChamber of Commerce President resigns
OL,4,Cover political donation
OL,6,FMr Madden made the donation while he
OL,7,Fwas vice president of the Chamber in
OL,8,FJanuary 2025.
OL,10,FHe told ITV News that the funds were
OL,11,Ffor a scoping project and were about
OL,12,Fbringing external expertise to the
OL,13,Fisland.
OL,15,FMr Madden declared the donation in a
OL,16,FChamber conflict of interest register
OL,17,Fearlier this year, which was then
OL,18,Fleaked, and he was called in front of
OL,19,Fthe Chamber's retail committee.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1780600264
OL,3,CChamber of Commerce President resigns
OL,4,Cover political donation
OL,6,FIt comes after one of Value Jersey's
OL,7,Fmain pledges to bring cheaper
OL,8,Fsupermarkets to the island like Aldi
OL,9,For Lidl.
OL,11,FIn a social media post, Mr Madden
OL,12,Fexplained: "I have not used my role to
OL,13,Fadvocate for any political movement,
OL,14,Fnor have I promoted any specific
OL,15,Fretail outcome or market entrant.
OL,17,F"My focus in office has always been on
OL,18,Frepresenting the broad interests of
OL,19,Four membership fairly, responsibly,
OL,20,Fand in good faith.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1780600264
OL,3,CChamber of Commerce President resigns
OL,4,Cover political donation
OL,6,F"However, leadership is not only about
OL,7,Fthe substance of your conduct, it is
OL,8,Falso about the confidence others have
OL,9,Fin your ability to carry out the role
OL,10,Feffectively.
OL,12,F"I recognise that the timing of that
OL,13,Fdeclaration has raised concerns and
OL,14,Fthat, particularly within the retail
OL,15,Fsector, it has led to a loss of
OL,16,Fconfidence in my position as President.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1780600264
OL,3,CChamber of Commerce President resigns
OL,4,Cover political donation
OL,6,F"While I do not accept that my conduct
OL,7,Fin office has been compromised, I do
OL,8,Faccept that confidence across all
OL,9,Fsectors is essential if the Chamber is
OL,10,Fto lead with credibility, balance, and
OL,11,Funity.
OL,13,F"If my continuing in the role risks
OL,14,Fbecoming a distraction from the
OL,15,FChamber's wider purpose and the
OL,16,Fimportant work it has to do on behalf
OL,17,Fof Jersey's business community, then
OL,18,Fit is right that I step aside.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
